Analyze Reports with Einstein Discovery for Reports

Einstein Discovery for Reports scans report data using artificial intelligence and statistical analysis. It explores patterns, identifies insights, and surfaces them in easy-to-understand charts.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in Lightning Experience
Available in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions.
Note: Requires CRM Analytics Plus license (extra cost).

Set Up Einstein Discovery for Reports
Enable CRM Analytics and assign Can Run Einstein Discovery for Reports permission to users. Analyze Report Data
Let Einstein Discovery for Reports augment your report with AI-powered insights into data.
